transcript.comment: Language of Caregivers Mother South Shore , Massachusetts (has an r+less dialect; dialect overall similar to RI) Father Semi+Standard American English (originally from Rutland , Massachusetts located in center of the state) , sometimes shows evidence of an r+less dialect; vowel quality is generally like that of SAE.
